I get "File access denied." when pressing the "Team OTA" button.

I found out that amlib.dll was readonly. After doing this with admin privileges, the patch worked:

attrib -r "C:Program FilesAdobeAdobe Premiere Pro CS6amlib.dll"

I got file access denied on the patch, but then I clicked disable activation then checked my premiere pro and it was activated (purple) It does it automatically somehow, Thanks, works with updates as well. Follow the video but don't worry about the patch as it will show file access denied
